ill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=290.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   MAGE vs. NECRO---Whos the best Solo Artist?</span><hr size=1> I have a question I am SURE will get much attention.  I started a Necro because I love to solo and was told from a few close friends that they are the CHAMPS at soloing.  And so far, I find that to be true, although I am still only a 14th level DE Necro.  But I am concerned that my time might be better spent starting a Mage...so I have been spending ALOT of time reading up on Mages.  <br>
<br>
Question is...what are major differences between the 2 classes?  Are the Mage's pets better then a Necro's?  Can Mage's do more damage then a Necro of the same level?  <br>
<br>
And lastly, I see alot of threads that comment on the fact that Mages are not very sought after for major raids...do Necro's have the same problem?<br>
<br>
Thank you in advance for your responses... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ufazzywabbithugger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fazzy Wabbithugger</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/01 8:31:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=290.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Necro's versus Mages</span><hr size=1> Each classes have there own advantages Gjakar, the way to play your character will determine how good your character is. <br>
<br>
 Now if we take Necro's and magicians. Here i will attempt to make list the advantages and disadvantage of both classes.<br>
<br>
Pets..<br>
<br>
  There is no comparaison to a magicians pet and to a necromancer's pet. We all know that magicians pets are superior than nec's pet and for that is the reason of our class. We are a class that relies on our pet !! If our pet dies, then we are doomed !  So this is why our pet have the most Hp's and other abilities that skeletons pets dont have !   Magicians pets will gain Dual weild at level 24 while necro's pets will get it at 29 ! This makes a BIG difference in my opinion ! <br>
<br>
Spells..<br>
<br>
  Now this is where the biggest difference exists, necro's spells are more suiting to soloing, hence ( darkness line of spells who works as a snare and a Dot at higher level )and the fear spell ! There is also the mana regeneration line of spell combines with the Lifetap, makes Necro's a much better class to solo with ! <br>
  On the other hand, because the magician spells are a Direct spell, the mob will loose it's health right away and not like the necro's dots which some takes up to 3 minutes to have dealt the full damage ! So i would think that a magician will kill the mob way faster than the necro, but downtime will keep us meditating a bit more ! <br>
<br>
  My magician is only level 40, and thus i dont know how magicians are used in big raids or the like but from what i read. Instead of being a Attack class we became, just like necro's a support class !  Meaning by this is that our only defender, our pets are banned in the planes, for reasons like bad pathing or the danger of having a pet on the loose. It's kinda sad but i think thats how it works. I read that we magicians have mostly the job of creating mod rods, Mod rods are summoned item that will convert some health to mana instantly when right clicked !  In order to keep the clerics FOM always we need to summon several of those to the clerics disposal. Other times we will be put on Malised duty, which is the act of casting a debuff on the mob !!  (( Only 2 class can cast Malise type of spell being, shaman's and mages )). <br>
<br>
  For the necro in the planes i think their role is pretty limited to being a mana pump.  Transfer their mana to clerics or nuking classes ! <br>
<br>
So to finish this, i'm gonna say that necro's are the best soloing class because of the Fear, snare, mana regenration type of spells.. But never underestimate the power of a Magician.. they might suprise you.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
