Necros are much better soloers (outdoors).  Our pets are better (stronger, more HP, etc.), but necros have fear, mez, root, lich, DoTs, FD - and the list goes on.  They were designed, it appears, to solo.  Mage can kill MUCH faster, but soloing is harder, with more downtime.  We solo by dishing out as much damage as quickly as we can.  Necros solo by killing steadily, with almost no fear of death.  Necros actually can dish out a lot more damage over time, but we dish out a lot more damage quickly.<br>
<br>
So overall - no question, necros win for soloing hands down.<br>
<br>
Bards are pretty good at soloing after level 35 or so, they get DoTs, DD, snare, stun, super sow, fear, charm, mez, etc.  So they have all the tools, but they are so wanted in groups they don't need to solo that much. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uonyxrosevalsharess.showPublicProfile?language=EN>OnyxroseValSharess</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 81<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/01 1:33:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=290.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: MAGE vs. NECRO---Whos the best Solo Artist?</span><hr size=1> Well, as I summed it up on our Guild Board...<br>
<br>
&quot;Use a Mage when you want it killed NOW, use a Necro when you want it killed SOON.&quot;<br>
<br>
It takes a Necro a good 4-5 minutes to kill a monster that would take a Mage 1-1.5 minutes.  Yes, DoTs do LOTS of damage... over a long time.  While that Mob is slowly bleeding, its hitting the pets for lots and lots... which is why the Necro Fears his way through exp.  <br>
<br>
Soloing for Necros can only be done outdoors, in the wide open zones.  Magicians solo well outside, but we can also solo indoors where the exp bonuses are higher.<br>
<br>
My last point is, you don't want to spend your time soloing!  Get in a group so you learn group dynamics; thats one reason why a lot of Necros dont do well on raids, they've spent so little time with others that they dont know the other class's strengths!<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uoctella.showPublicProfile?language=EN>octella</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(8/2/01 3:25:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=290.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   re</span><hr size=1> everyone pretty much sums it up, but i'd like to add 1 point.<br>
