<br>
I have wound up pulling for <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Necro</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> partners, and I have been pretty much able to pull continuously.  I pull with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Maliso</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> and make sure it sticks, bring 'em in, and then the necro takes over.  The occasional nuke when the mob threatens to run too far, and we are rocking.<br>
